    <item>
      <title>Gul’dan – an orc warlock</title>
      <link>https://artbrushray.github.io/posts/guldan/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Feb 2023 21:45:14 +0300</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://artbrushray.github.io/posts/guldan/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi everyone!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I want to show you my new Warcraft fan art and to tell a small story behind it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My love to computer games started with Starcraft. Later then when I discovered digital art, Starcraft and Warcraft were among the major sources of inspiration&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Needless to say I raved about the idea of making art for the Blizzard&amp;hellip; many did. But man, how good one have to be to work with them. It was too much and too big for one small enthusiast who haven&amp;rsquo;t even seen an art school.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
